### 4.3 Contraindications

Hypersensitivity to {{ drug.name }}, any other penicillin, or any of the excipients. History of severe hypersensitivity reaction (e.g., anaphylaxis) to another beta-lactam antibiotic (e.g., a cephalosporin, carbapenem, or monobactam).
